YAML
Step 1: Select manufacturer and item type. Set the item level (default: 50).
Range: 1-50
Step 2: Select the mainPartBarrel. Must match manufacturer and item type.

Select two skins to auto-generate a hybrid mix added into Special Skins.

Step 3: Select the skin.
Hybrid multi-layer skins (Special Skins) are available below.
Step 4: Select the element (optional). Leave blank for no element.
Step 5: Add legendary perks and/or normal parts. You can add multiple parts and adjust quantities. Parts can be applied to all items regardless of item type.
Step 6: Important! some guns require specific parts to function correctly such as barell, grip, scope, magazine which can be seen in the list below but also this information can be found in the deserialization spreadsheet here: Item building guide select Parts below by clicking manufacturer and parts you need/want to add
